Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:50.27,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Eu não devia ter dito aquilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:53.27,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Estou satisfeita depois de ver \Num novo lado da Koharun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.03,0:10:53.15,Main Dialogue Top,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.43,Main Dialogue,Hiina,0000,0000,0000,,A Koharun estava ótima daquele jeito.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:56.86,Main Dialogue,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Sim. Estava perfeita!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:59.05,Main Dialogue,Yua,0000,0000,0000,,Ótima Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:02.67,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Sério, parem de me apelidar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:05.08,Main Dialogue,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,É sempre assim!
